melihat Chi Cheng.

503
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,560
Why do you seem unhappy?

504
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,680
Saya tidak tahu.

505
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,640
I am just a bit flustered.

506
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,280
Mungkin sudah terlalu lama
sejak terakhir kali saya melihatnya.

507
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,800
Who is here?

508
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:36,880
Anda akan tahu saat Anda melihatnya.

509
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,640
Have a seat.

510
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,240
Mengapa Anda menurunkan berat badan?

511
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,720
Did you miss me?

512
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:42,040
Bagaimana menurutmu?

513
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:44,520
Bagaimana saya tahu?

514
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:50,280
I missed you.

515
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,880
Apakah Anda merindukan saya?

516
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:55,960
I did.

517
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:58,600
How much?

518
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,280
I missed you so much...

519
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,480
bahwa saya menyerahkan
perbendaharaan kecil saya.

520
00:33:10,120 --> 00:33:11,120
What did you say?

521
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:13,520
Itu bukan apa -apa.

522
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:16,280
Your case will go
to trial in two days.

523
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,360
Selain perbendaharaan kecil,

524
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:22,720
what else did you give up?

525
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,440
Rumah tua itu.

526
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,520
Why didn't you sell my house?

527
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:45,200
Saya tidak ingin keluarga
Anda memandang rendah saya.

528
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,880
Then borrow money from Cheng Yu.

529
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:50,000
Itu karena kami
berdua adalah keluarga.

530
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,720
You always said...

531
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,320
Saya seorang pelengkap...

532
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,560
who doesn't spend anything.

533
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:04,320
Kali ini, saya menghabiskan segalanya.

534
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,360
Let's see how you can
diss me in the future.

535
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,600
Anda adalah pemodal saya.

536
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:14,960
As long as you come
back, I can make money.

537
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,960
Jika Anda tinggal di sini, saya
akan menderita kerugian terbesar.

538
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:19,600
So after calculating it,

539
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,320
Lebih baik membuat Anda keluar dari sini.

540
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,680
Actually, I regret it too.

541
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:44,720
Saya seharusnya memberi Anda
lebih banyak uang saku saat itu.

542
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:48,400
Now that I have given the
money to other people, I realize...

543
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:51,600
10 atau 20 yuan itu benar
-benar bukan apa -apa.

544
00:34:53,120 --> 00:34:54,120
Actually,

545
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,240
my little treasury
is for our retirement.

546
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,360
Jika Anda tidak bisa keluar,

547
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:04,520
Apa gunanya uang itu untuk saya?

548
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:06,760
So...

549
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,680
I am not buying your freedom.

550
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,120
Saya membeli keamanan saya sendiri.

551
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,960
You know what?

552
00:35:12,961 --> 00:35:15,600
Ketika saya tidur di rumah sendirian
sekarang, saya merasa sangat takut.

553
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,000
I just want you to come back.

554
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,439
Saya tidak ingin kehidupan mewah.

555
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,640
I only want you.

556
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,360
Chi Cheng.

557
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,040
Say something.

558
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,440
Chi Cheng!

559
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,120
Say something.

560
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,160
Aku membencimu.

561
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,400
Lihatmu.
You still have over 10 minutes.

562
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:47,480
Hei, dia kembali ke selnya.

563
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:48,560
You should go too.

564
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:13,519
(Sel penjara)

565
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:14,680
1706.

566
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,800
Saatnya makan.

